  "instructions": [
    "Mix together mustard oil, ginger, garlic, and green chilies in a small bowl.",
    "Heat the mixture in a pan over medium heat for 2 minutes.",
    "Add curry powder and salt-free seasoning and stir for 1 minute.",
    "In a separate pan, heat the pasta water over low heat for 5 minutes.",
    "Add lemon juice and chopped cilantro to the pasta water and stir.",
    "Warm the ti-leaf wraps in the pan with the pasta water mixture for 1 minute.",
    "Assemble the wraps by spreading a small amount of the mustardy mixture on each wrap, followed by a sprinkle of unsalted pistachio and a drizzle of the pasta water mixture.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
